('Judges', 12, 'kids', 2, 'What word could the Ephraimites not pronounce correctly at the fords of Jordan?', 'Shibboleth', 'Tabernacle', 'Gilead', 'Bethlehem', 'a', 'Judges 12:6 — "Then said they unto him, Say now Shibboleth: and he said Sibboleth: for he could not frame to pronounce it right."'),
