('Judges', 13, 'kids', 2, 'What appeared to Manoah''s wife to announce the birth of Samson?', 'An angel of the LORD', 'A pillar of fire', 'A dove from heaven', 'A still small voice', 'a', 'Judges 13:3 — "And the angel of the LORD appeared unto the woman, and said unto her, Behold now, thou art barren, and bearest not: but thou shalt conceive, and bear a son."'),
