('Judges', 14, 'kids', 2, 'What did Samson find inside the dead lion when he returned?', 'A swarm of bees and honey', 'A nest of birds', 'A fox and its cubs', 'Ants and their food', 'a', 'Judges 14:8 — "And after a time he returned to take her, and he turned aside to see the carcase of the lion: and, behold, there was a swarm of bees and honey in the carcase of the lion."'),
